Package model

Class Repeater

  • java.lang.Object
    • model.Piece
      • model.Repeater
  • public class Repeater
extends Piece
    The Repeater class provides the PlantsVSZombie game with a single Piece type that once called can create a Repeater Piece in of itself. This class only contains a constructor and simplifies the Piece class code. It uses its super class Piece to create a new object and passes it's designated parameters. A Repeater plant doubles the attack damage and cost of a normal peashooter.
    Version:
    4.0
    Author:
    RG, Ryan Boucher
